{"tid":1358841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老尾今朝地鐵塞撚到唔駛返工咁...","createTime":"2019-07-24T04:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:03:55.000Z","uid":127381,"like":105,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e09d1802cfd6f8035eeccbe917deb3fe528bab1c","tid":1358841,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我支持你地</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續不合作運動唔好俾佢停！<br />\n<br />\n另外我想同各位受阻既市民講：<br />\n- 如果你有睇連登而冇提早起身搭車，係你on9唔關班年輕人事<br />\n- 如果你乜都唔知，咁抵你一世做港豬，因為就算你入左新界俾人打都唔會知咩事第日如常返工<br />\n- 如果你話遲到就俾公司炒，咁一係你公司仆街一係就係你廢公司想炒你好耐。如果連轉工既能力都冇即係都係你廢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：今朝收左第二封warning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9538cefc9e17a012fa298c844f0625a0d58b74","tid":1358841,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881d3b0fe7a33c79bf54b98ac5a0c7c3b1d657cf","tid":1358841,"uid":82253,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"打算番工又想支持下不合作既和理優：<br />\n可以&ldquo;傾電話&rdquo; 講下野<br />\n例如<br />\n唉呀 我未番到公司呀 不過呢 都唔怪得佢地既 鬼叫之前港鐵做幫兇 個D人命嚟架 我地遲番下算D乜"},{"pid":"4fa06f1bd44783f64535b1977d338add0e91d71f","tid":1358841,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09d1802cfd6f8035eeccbe917deb3fe528bab1c","tid":1358841,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我支持你地</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ki